{
  "id": "scifi-transmission",
  "name": "星际传输讯息",
  "category": "scifi",
  "description": "一条来自星际的传输讯息，带有科幻风格的信号编码",
  "trigger": {
    "type": "random",
    "probability": 0.02,
    "conditions": [
      {
        "type": "setting",
        "operator": "contains",
        "value": "科幻|星际|太空|宇宙|外星|飞船",
        "description": "科幻或星际场景可能触发"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variables": {
    "signalId": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "信号编号"
    },
    "source": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "信号来源"
    },
    "destination": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "信号目的地"
    },
    "timestamp": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "时间戳"
    },
    "content": {
      "type": "text",
      "maxLength": 400,
      "description": "讯息内容"
    },
    "signalType": {
      "type": "string",
      "default": "紧急",
      "options": ["常规", "紧急", "警告", "求救"],
      "description": "信号类型"
    }
  },
  "promptTemplate": "请生成一条星际传输讯息。\n\n背景信息：\n- 来源：{{source}}\n- 目的地：{{destination}}\n- 场景：{{scene}}\n- 信号类型：{{signalType}}\n\n要求：\n1. 使用科幻风格的通讯语言\n2. 可以包含坐标、时间、技术术语\n3. 内容要简洁有力，符合紧急通讯格式\n4. 字数控制在100-250字之间\n\n请直接输出讯息内容，不要有其他说明。",
  "style": {
    "theme": "scifi",
    "colors": ["#0a0a1a", "#00ff88", "#0088ff"],
    "mood": "科技未来"
  },
  "rarity": "rare",
  "collectible": true
}